! Block quotes

Single-line form with `>`; repeat the marker to nest:

> Single-line block quote
> Continues the quote
>> Nested block quote
>>> Deeper nesting

Extended form with `<<<`, optionally carrying one or more CSS classes, and able
to contain several paragraphs:

<<<.tc-tiddler-frame.myclass
Extended block quote with dot-separated CSS classes.

It can span multiple paragraphs.
<<<

<<<
Plain extended block quote without a class.
<<<

