! Code blocks

A fenced code block with a language tag is highlighted for that language:

```javascript
function add(a, b) {
	return a + b; // highlighted as JavaScript
}
```

A fenced block without a language tag is plain preformatted text:

```
plain preformatted text
no language highlighting
```

Typed blocks render their content as the given content type:

$$$text/css
.foo { color: red; }
$$$

$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki
This is ''wikitext'' rendered inside a typed block.
$$$

! Links

* CamelCase auto-link: HelloThere
* Suppress a CamelCase link with a tilde: ~HelloThere
* Pretty link: [[Some Tiddler]]
* Pretty link with display text: [[Display text|Some Tiddler]]
* External link: https://tiddlywiki.com
* External pretty link: [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com]]
* Mail link: mailto:someone@example.com
* System link: [[$:/SiteTitle]]

! Images

An [img[Motovun Jack.jpg]] image, and one with attributes:
[img width=64 class="tc-image" [Motovun Jack.jpg]].

! Transclusions

* Whole tiddler: {{HelloThere}}
* With a template: {{HelloThere||$:/core/ui/ViewTemplate}}
* A field of the current tiddler: {{!!title}}
* A field of another tiddler: {{HelloThere!!modified}}

! Comments

A WikiText comment is not rendered:

<!-- This is a comment -->
